	Known for being a perfectionist, Streep said she studied violin  
for two months before shooting began. 
</P>
<P>
	``I am much less attentive to detail in my work than I was in  
the past. I don't consider this positive but this way I am able to 
spend more time with my children,'' Streep told the Italian news 
agency ANSA. 
</P>
